# Zerodha Clone 🧾📈

A full-stack stock trading web application inspired by Zerodha. Built using the MERN stack with live stock price integration.

## 🚀 Features

- 🔒 User authentication with JWT
- 📊 Dashboard with stock performance data
- 💹 Buy/Sell functionality
- 👁️ Watchlist and holdings
- 📡 Live stock price integration using Finnhub API
- 🧠 (Upcoming) AI-based stock recommendation

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

**Frontend**: React, Tailwind CSS, React Router  
**Backend**: Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, JWT  
**APIs**: Finnhub API  
**Version Control**: Git, GitHub

## 📦 Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Dhanu0746/Zerodha-clone.git

# Frontend
cd frontend
npm install
npm start

# Backend
cd backend
npm install
npm start
